# AnesBuddy
Your digital peripheral brain. Essential safety checklists, rapid clinical calculators, and drug references designed for the modern anesthesia provider
AnesBuddy is the centralized educational resource designed to replace the clutter of physical pocket guides and disparate websites. Built by anesthesia providers for anesthesia providers, this app aggregates high-yield safety tools into one clean, offline-accessible interface.

Key Features:

Rapid Calculators: Instantly compute fluid management, allowable blood loss, and drug dosing adjustments without the mental math.

Crisis Checklists: Quick-reference algorithms for difficult airways, malignant hyperthermia, and pre-op safety checks.

Drug Reference: Searchable library of standard pharmacological data and reference ranges.

Intuitive Design: High-contrast, large-text interface designed for quick readability in the operating room environment.

AnesBuddy is an educational reference tool intended to support, not replace, clinical judgment.
